text_raw:
2. The 3rd day of October 2022 is appointed as the day on which the 
Judicial Council Act 2019 (No. 33 of 2019), in so far as it is not already in 
operation, shall come into operation. 

GIVEN under my Official Seal, 

30 September, 2022. 

HELEN MCENTEE, 
Minister for Justice. 

Notice of the making of this Statutory Instrument was published in 
“Iris Oifigiúil” of 7th October, 2022.

EXPLANATORY NOTE 

(This note is not part of the Instrument and does not purport to be a legal 
interpretation.) 

This Order brings into operation those provisions of the Judicial Council Act 
2019 concerning judicial conduct and ethics which are not already in operation. 
The provisions come into operation on 3 October 2022.
